reviewText: OBSEASON 1, 5 STARS. OBSEASON 2, 3 STARS. OBS2's plot began to frazzle. People acted out of character. Many scenes were just filler, with no reason or purpose. Watch season 1 and stop there. It's worth it.
This show really brought the creative minds aspect back to television for me. In a world consumed with the drama of reality shows, it was nice to see a tv series take a turn.
